# Go source MUST be LF: `gofmt -l` flags CRLF, and CI runners check out with autocrlf (which would otherwise
# make the .go files CRLF and fail the installer's gofmt gate). Force LF for Go regardless of platform.
*.go text eol=lf

# Workflow YAML MUST be LF too: release.yml has a `shell: bash` step, and CRLF (from autocrlf checkout) would
# put stray \r into the bash script -- breaking `set -euo pipefail` and the tag comparisons. Force LF.
*.yml text eol=lf
